P03 Lead Qualification Analysis

# Prompt 3 – Lead Qualification Analysis

## Version 1 (v3.1)

### Prompt
Generic instruction with no structure and unclear, inconsistent lead analysis

### Change Made
Initial version

### Observed Effect
No actionable insights and not usable in CRM workflow

### Lesson Learned
Prompts must include clear classification criteria


## Version 2 (v3.2)

### Prompt
You are a B2B sales analyst and classify this lead: business type, stage (startup/scaling/established), conversion likelihood (Low/Medium/High), and next action. Input: [LEAD_TEXT]. Output JSON only.

### Change Made
Added role (B2B analyst), defined classification categories and enforced JSON output

### Observed Effect
Consistent, structured results and easily integrated into CRM systems

### Lesson Learned
Structured prompts and format constraints give usable business outputs
